{
  "stem": "19923.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- I spend six weeks sometimes at that place-- it was a-- like, a children's camp-- and participating in the sports.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I do recollect that I once was mischievous.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And just before leaving, for some reason I went into the toilet, and I slammed the toilet seat down.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by slamming the toilet seat down, the toilet broke.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So of course, they discovered immediately that I was the one responsible for breaking the toilet seat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, you're not-- they told me, you're not going home until your father pays for this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was worried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, my god, I'm going to be send here-- kept here for life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But fortunately, I was shipped home, and I didn't have to pay-- or my father didn't have to pay for the toilet seat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I remember, though, that that incident was something that stands out in my memory of Kreuznach.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although there were fond-- I have fond memories of the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did a lot of walking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a lot of music.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a very rural area, picturesque, just like you would see in the most picture postcards of the countryside of Germany, the heart of Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there, of course, you were away from all the tumult, the-- the tumult of the-- of the antisemitism that we experienced in the city, which was a constant thing on a daily basis.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I'll get to that a little later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that helped me in terms of developing my strength.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Also, it-- it motivated me to excel in sports.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because I felt in order to be strong, I had to do a lot of activities, and I excelled in soccer.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was-- I was very good because I was short.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
